So much has changed during this year. Its completely crazy to think that during only fee months of being stuck at home perspective changed so fucking much.

I felt scared to dive deep and be left with only a few things so I allowed myself a decent amount of options. I didn't wear more than half of them. It's fun to style looks in the parks but outside of the universe of the parks there is no real human need for a snow white dress and magic carpet purse.
